# ✅ 1️⃣ Add Mode Detection in `loadJSON()`

Add inside your existing `loadJSON()` after JSON parsing:

```javascript
// ---- 3.pdf Template Mode Detection ----

// Incident Resolution Summary (3.pdf version)
if (data.incident_number && data.impact?.impact_start && data.resolution) {
  switchMode('incidentresolution3');
}

// Major Incident Communications Pack
else if (data.major_incident_number && data.initial_notification) {
  switchMode('micomms');
}

// Weekly Operations / Incident Trends
else if (data.client_name && data.kpis && data.report_period) {
  switchMode('weeklyops');
}

// Integration Specification
else if (data.integration_name && data.systems && data.authentication) {
  switchMode('integrationspec');
}

// Technical Design (3.pdf version)
else if (data.story_id && data.design && data.data_model_changes) {
  switchMode('technicaldesign3');
}
```

